---
title: Shawarma-Inspired Beef Wraps with Crispy Shallots and Garlic Sauce
description: Ground beef is seared with our Shawarma Spice Blend for a meal full of sweet and smoky aromas!  We've got crunchy and tart pickled cabbage as well as a bright herb and garlic sauce, all that's left to say is YUM YUM!
